parameters:
[Fortune Teller] You... should defeat your detestable enemy as soon as
possible...
[Fortune Teller] It's better not to approach...
[Fortune Teller] Hehehe, you... to a prostitute...
[Fortune Teller] Right now, if you just keep moving...
[Fortune Teller] Something is about to happen...

[Fortune Teller] Once at the tavern... once at the warehouse... twice
on the street...
[Fortune Teller] It seems like I can make some money...
[Fortune Teller] Oh, finally becoming a prostitute... hehehehe
[Fortune Teller] Now is the time to work hard...
[Fortune Teller] First floor of the inn...
[Fortune Teller] Second floor of the school...
[Fortune Teller] What else could this be... a... small... child?
[Fortune Teller] There are quite a few of you...

[Fortune Teller] Soldiers of the guide, taverns on the surface, taverns
underground, men in the warehouse, men in the brothel, casino stages,
brothel clients, students of the academy, ...

[Fortune Teller] Be careful... the students of the academy... it's a
bad end.
[Fortune Teller] When you talk to a witch...
[Fortune Teller] But... there might also be good things...
[Fortune Teller] Now is... your last chance...
